KVM: nVMX: Use correct VPID02 when emulating L1 INVVPID

In case L0 didn't allocate vmx->nested.vpid02 for L2,
vmcs02->vpid is set to vmx->vpid.
Consider this case when emulating L1 INVVPID in L0.

